Subviewer 2.0
=============

  Extension:

    ".sub"

  Tags:

    <b>bold</b>
    <i>italic</i>
    <u>underline</u>

  Notes:

    COLF is "&H" followed by RRGGBB. STYLE is "st" for strikeout, "ud" for
    underline, "bd" for bold, or "it" for italic. SIZE is font size in
    points. FONT is font name.

  Source:

    http://forum.doom9.org/showthread.php?p=542288#post542288
